Comment: 0,0:00:01.06,0:00:01.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,[ProtivoTankovoye Ruzhyo Degtyaryova: A Russian anti-tank rifle.]
Comment: 0,0:00:01.06,0:00:01.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,[今月の目標 せめて先月分	This months goal: get at least a part of last months.]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.75,0:00:07.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,...can you hear this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.39,0:00:13.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If you're listening to this, then you're somehow related to Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.33,0:00:17.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If the past hasn't changed, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:24.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:26.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not blaming you for shooting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.85,0:00:28.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't shoot, Suou!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.24,0:00:31.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:33.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.22,0:00:36.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:48.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That sucked big time! Support, my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.95,0:00:51.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No one wants that homo side-gag-character!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:53.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Really, they've got to be kidding us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.64,0:00:57.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Just when I was in a good mood and everything was going right, shit had to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.29,0:01:00.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! That director won't be getting away with this that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.84,0:01:05.44,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.91,0:01:07.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't she look like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.22,0:01:12.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You know, "Maurice of the Rose: The Crying Jar and Elephant's Trunk!".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.45,0:01:14.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Caravaggio from that movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.31,0:01:14.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.63,0:01:17.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The one with the sick, psycho-lover vibes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.47,0:01:23.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she indeed looks sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:25.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We have to take her home, Kiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:27.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I'm not into little girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.45,0:01:29.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, that's a crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.03,0:01:30.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Go and get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.98,0:01:39.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yikes! That pink haired girl!
