Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.25,0:03:47.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We found it on the roof of a building that was 100m southeast of the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:52.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We've also found the empty 14.5mm cartridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:55.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A PTRD, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.03,0:04:02.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Can we conclude that it was materialized by Izanagi's power?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:07.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't even confirmed whether that kid is Izanagi or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:09.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Or even what the kid's gender is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:12.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So we have to strip the kid naked, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:14.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Is that kid just a decoy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:18.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean the real Izanagi is somewhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:20.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps he's already in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:23.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at that PTRD.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.71,0:04:27.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The scope and bolt are on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:31.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The kid in Vladivostok wasn't left-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.84,0:04:37.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We can't rule out the possibility that Izanagi and Professor Pavlichenko could be here already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:40.27,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they're planning to regroup in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:44.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,BK201 won't necessarily have the same plan in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:48.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The first thing he's going to chase after coming to Tokyo is most likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:50.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Izanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:57.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:05:00.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:02.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say this is the best choice,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:05.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,but it's better than making your cold worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:07.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:08.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Does someone you know live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:10.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can't really say that I know them...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:13.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Saying this hurts a little, but they aren't bad people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.97,0:05:16.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You can't come out yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:21.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,...I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.22,0:05:25.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Messier code: UB001. Amber.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:28.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A contractor who has the memories of the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:36.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Leader of the contractor terrorist organization EPR.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:39.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A former member of the MI6.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:43.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There is also evidence that suggests she acted with BK201 in the Heaven's War.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:47.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know much about her back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:50.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But she saw everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:59.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,As well as what came after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.26,0:06:03.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can easily get the CD if you're working for them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:06.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Open that with an analysis program.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:12.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The keyword is Izanami.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:13.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Izanami...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:27.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So these are... the Mitaka documents?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:30.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to read them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:32.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And tell them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:35.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hei will be at the end of that path.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:37.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You need to tell them, so they won't make any mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.66,0:06:45.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,T-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:49.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please. No need to thank us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:53.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You were nice enough to give me clothes to change into.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.19,0:06:54.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And on top of that, such nice clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.90,0:06:57.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She's really happy about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:58.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You don't see that everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Could she be a natural-born cosplayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.36,0:07:02.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is our good deed for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:05.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say we go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:07.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sounds great! Where should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:09.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ikebukuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:12.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She has great taste, I'm telling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:14.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She just asked to go visit Ikebukuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:18.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps she has been always wanting to walk the Maiden Road when she was in Russia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.97,0:07:20.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, those pictures are awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:22.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So your mother is a photographer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:26.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It would be great if she can come with us to the next event to take more pictures!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:27.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:29.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She's just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:31.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like we can ask for a professional to show up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:34.27,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:37.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I was separated from her when I was still a young child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:43.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! You made me cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:45.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.89,0:07:48.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You traversed through borders to find your mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:51.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The further away someone is, the dearer they become.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:55.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:57.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What does it look like? A flying squirrel, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:07:58.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Momonga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:02.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's just that it's staring at me with a wicked look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.17,0:08:05.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you pissed him off in your previous life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:09.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's go and find her mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:11.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... it's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:12.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's not going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:14.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:16.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What were those tears for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:19.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Those are two different things altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:25.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We're professionals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:27.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We won't work for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:30.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She wouldn't be here if she had money!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:32.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, aren't we partners?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:37.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try ripping them off with your usual tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:40.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Don't badmouth me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:41.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:46.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I have some money, so get me to Ikebukuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:50.27,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Roger! We'll do anything in our power to find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.27,0:08:52.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This is a tear-jerking, special reunion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:54.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:55.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.55,0:09:02.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Tokyo is nothing like Russia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:05.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Man, this place sure has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:10.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. Looks like she isn't there either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:12.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She hadn't been back for a while, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:14.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's going to be a real problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.60,0:09:15.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.77,0:09:17.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Not to worry. We've still got something up our sleeves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.26,0:09:19.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the next place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:20.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:26.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Are they harassing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:29.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why does the editor of that photobook have such a cat-filled place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.08,0:09:31.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He just changed his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:34.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The publication industry was hit by the bad economy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.19,0:09:39.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If she hasn't stopped there, she's probably at a photo shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:41.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A photo shoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:43.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's a real pain when she's at a photo shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:48.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She has a fondness for freedom, like a cat. She would wander off somewhere and you could never find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:50.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of pictures has she been taking lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:52.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:55.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, she seems to be obsessed about the Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:57.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:58.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:09:59.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:00.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Got what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:04.13,DTB-Overlap,,0,0,0,,I see it, I see it, I see it now...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:12.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.87,0:10:14.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, that's so lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:18.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the Buddha's last moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:21.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you hiding Izanami's whereabouts even from us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.44,0:10:29.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If BK201 finds out where Izanami is located, he will definitely go after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:34.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Now that BK201 has lost his powers, he's merely a gloomy gigolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.62,0:10:38.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot throw this chance away if we want to catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:41.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I never expected you two would be in agreement about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:45.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really hiding it just from you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.75,0:10:49.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone who's been in contact with her has had their memories erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:53.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There are only a few people, including me, who know her whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:59.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I would imagine that no one will be able to see her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:02.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, he's really a party-pooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:05.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:10.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You feeling warm down there because you can't see him, despite the fact he's so close?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:15.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go and search a bit more in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:22.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe someone else other than the Director might know where Izanami is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.92,0:11:28.54,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We can't rule out that BK201 won't do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:32.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see BK201.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.64,0:11:36.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But if I were to trust the Mikata Documents...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.97,0:11:41.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Izanagi looks at the false bottom of the sea, waiting for Izanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:46.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Izanami will eventually cross it, and those two will meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:52.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,When they meet, Heaven and Earth will be split asunder,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.82,0:11:56.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,and the Hell's Gate will appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:59.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,From there will come something alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:01.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And conflicts will continue forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:03.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Such an abstract story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:10.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But I have a bad feeling about the meeting of Izanagi and Izanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:13.94,Title,,0,0,0,,Episode 9    The Meeting Comes Suddenly One Day...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:18.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:22.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to meet my mother that badly when I was young...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:24.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:27.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How many kilometers do you think we need to walk to find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:29.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You got a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.42,0:12:31.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hold your horses, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:33.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:39.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.72,0:12:42.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She took the picture from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:46.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Her mother will come back here for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:49.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But the photo album is out already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:50.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You've still got a lot to learn, Kiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:52.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She already started with this theme.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:54.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She won't be done until the construction is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Both photographers and detectives are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.39,0:12:58.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's what makes a professional different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:13:00.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So when will she come back? How long do I need to wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:04.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Overseas?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:06.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Like another country?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:08.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tough luck, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.94,0:13:12.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She usually reserves a room a week before her shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:14.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know when she'll be back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:16.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:19.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She isn't really a resident here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.76,0:13:25.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there is a room that's freed up, though. What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:35.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Mom stood here and took the photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:37.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:39.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suou.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:45.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So you're Suou-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:47.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Um... who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:50.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You want to meet your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:55.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A good woman can read other people's hearts after a certain age.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:58.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding. That's absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:14:03.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother will be returning to Japan tonight at eight o'clock, at Haneda airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:05.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:08.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to have someone you want to see again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:12.54,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to meet you. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.27,0:14:18.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you really want to meet now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:23.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I want to meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.31,0:14:30.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Things don't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:32.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom's gone overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:34.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She's coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:36.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,On a plane that lands at eight o'clock tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:37.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.59,0:14:38.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.97,0:14:40.27,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you run into her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:44.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't see anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:51.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hopefully we'll find something here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.02,0:14:53.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:57.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hazuki and Youko are supposed to go to Haneda, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.95,0:15:01.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I heard it was to pick up some goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:04.72,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That information has been leaked!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:07.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Over here! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.52,0:15:09.21,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.21,0:15:11.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to rush! She won't be here before eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:17.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, can you really trust that woman you supposedly met on the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:21.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,As long as it's not coming from your mouth, it's safe to assume that it isn't wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:23.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You little bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.66,0:15:26.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. Please wait here for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:29.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll call you when it's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:31.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:45.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you forget about your grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:47.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:52.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I kicked you out of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:56.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:02.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.66,0:16:04.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:15.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother Mizue doesn't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.46,0:16:19.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you go and see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:22.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be that flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:26.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get to see her when that plane lands!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:30.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, your heart is racing already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:31.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Racing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:34.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for pointing out the obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:36.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,After that much sprinting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:39.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:45.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I know that too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:50.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You should know that contractors don't feel anything toward their relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:55.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If you had hated me for that and kicked me out, I would have forgiven you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:57.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I am your...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:17:04.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No... I was destined to walk the path of the underworld as a mere servant of a silly lineage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.95,0:17:11.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,After becoming a contractor, I've realized for the first time how stupid it was to put my life in jeopardy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:14.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I hated you because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:19.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no longer your puppet. Simple as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:26.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're Sawasaki-sama from the Ministry of Internal Affairs and Communications, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:27.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:31.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's ready. Please come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.98,0:17:40.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So you're not going to forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:44.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,When I heard that I could see you again, I had some hopes for you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:47.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:50.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Youko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:52.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Did she just leave? Aren't you with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:02.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Um... are we in the right building?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.63,0:18:07.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:15.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:25.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:34.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Li-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:23.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Put Youko down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:27.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Neither of us will have the advantage if you're carrying the hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:28.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.43,0:19:44.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.25,0:19:46.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:50.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How could he see through me that easily?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:51.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Did I drop my guard...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.26,0:19:53.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No... was I distracted?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:55.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:19:59.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They said there's some trouble on the runway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:03.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:05.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if I don't meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:06.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.38,0:20:07.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you so excited a moment ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.09,0:20:12.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.85,0:20:15.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There is... there is no God!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.82,0:20:23.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Look! Even this old fart with terrible body odor dreams of his mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:29.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't anyone who wouldn't be happy to see their mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.69,0:20:49.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:56.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:58.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.27,0:21:02.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I missed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.88,0:21:10.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.82,0:21:13.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, it's the tear-jerking scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.22,0:21:16.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It would be uncomfortable to stay any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:19.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Their affection isn't some kind of reality show.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.43,0:21:23.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's something everyone holds dear to them, deep inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.39,0:21:31.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, you've become a splendid adult to say that, Matsukichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.42,0:21:32.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.49,0:21:36.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Gah! How do you know my real name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.18,0:21:38.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.17,0:21:45.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy, Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.40,0:22:00.90,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Kureteku yuubae ni senaka osarete
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.40,0:22:00.90,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}My back is pressed by the darkening glow of dusk
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.06,0:22:11.41,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Arukidasu kage ga shimesu hou e
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.06,0:22:11.41,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I start walking toward where my shadow points
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.41,0:22:20.97,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Taenai ikutsu mo no deai to wakare o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.41,0:22:20.97,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Repeating the many, ceaseless encounters and partings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.10,0:22:27.15,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Kurikaeshi doko e mukau no ka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.10,0:22:27.15,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Where do I head to?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.90,0:22:32.25,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Hito wa dare mo mayoinagara
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.90,0:22:32.25,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}For all people, while they are lost,
Dialogue: 2,0:22:31.88,0:22:37.01,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}tsumi to iu na no sadame o seotte
Dialogue: 2,0:22:31.88,0:22:37.01,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}they bear the fate known as sin
Dialogue: 3,0:22:36.78,0:22:45.66,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Sore de mo nao ikiru imi o shiru darou
Dialogue: 3,0:22:36.78,0:22:45.66,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Nevertheless, I'll still learn of the meaning to live, right?
Dialogue: 4,0:22:45.48,0:22:50.75,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Bokura wa sou Day by Day
Dialogue: 4,0:22:45.48,0:22:50.75,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}That's right, Day by Day,
Dialogue: 5,0:22:50.49,0:22:57.70,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ashita e tsuzuku michi no tochuu de
Dialogue: 5,0:22:50.49,0:22:57.70,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}we're midway on the road leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 6,0:22:57.33,0:23:05.29,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Now Say It Again kimi to futari no mama
Dialogue: 6,0:22:57.33,0:23:05.29,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Now Say It Again, though it'd be great if
Dialogue: 7,0:23:05.21,0:23:15.58,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}irareta nara ii no ni naa...
Dialogue: 7,0:23:05.21,0:23:15.58,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I could remain together with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.36,0:23:20.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.16,0:23:22.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you like, Shion?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.31,0:23:26.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You got it wrong again, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.94,0:23:28.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because of my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.94,0:23:30.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not Shion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:36.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.53,0:23:39.44,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, I'm Suou!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.49,0:23:42.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.10,0:23:44.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're not Suou!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.92,0:23:46.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be her...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.68,0:23:52.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,because she died... eight years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.69,0:24:03.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,When she was about to learn the truth, there was nothing left.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.71,0:24:07.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, father...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.15,0:24:09.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,the memories of her siblings, everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.51,0:24:13.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,When she knew everything was a lie,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.32,0:24:14.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,she begins to run into a dark cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.64,0:24:17.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Into the void of nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.73,0:24:21.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Seeking for the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.44,0:24:23.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Just running recklessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.95,0:24:28.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And then... she holds onto something.